---
title: Seared Pork Steak & Sage Butter with Potato Chunks & Sautéed Veggies
description: The secret is in the sauce but don’t worry because we’re sharing our saucy secrets right here. It’s a buttery sage delight tonight, perfect for
coating over pan seared pork, sliced and ready for eating as soon as it hits your table.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
